{"title":"曾在雪天想起英雄","authors":["斗峰"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾在雪天想起英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪是温柔的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从《沁园春》里下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄伫立长城之外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铮铮铁骨咏叹历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评说秦皇汉武"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪飘洒下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个湖南的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见了孟姜女哭倒长城时的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情状"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪下着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红装素裹洒出最漂亮的一笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄揎袖挥毫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一笔已久的酝酿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼出二万五千里的气势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让后人临摹和阅读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"户外风雪交作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平仄的枪炮声此起彼伏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的抽烟姿势镇定自若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立在地图边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把中国的江山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨星陨落了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄再也看不见雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代的雪在社会主义的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然飘落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪的品格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导着诗人国度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为这个时代学习的典范"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缅怀英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们重新读到有关雪的章节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀念此时无声无息地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着眼前的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘然而落"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}